Scripts for Windows cmd.exe
===========================

Scripts and shortcuts mostly for working in Windows cmd.exe.

Process

    > ps

	Interactive process viewer/killer.

	needs: [fzf]

Apps

    > scoopfz [update]

	Interactive scoop browser. Search, install and uninstall scoop apps.
	`update` runs `scoop update *` and updates the scoopfz database.

	Not aware of changes when installing or uninstalling at this time. Exit
	and run `scoopfz update` to refresh the database.

	needs: [scoop, fzf, Ruby]


    > get-blender-alpha

	Download and unzip the latest Blender alpha.  Also create a cli
	command `blender-alpha`.  Manually configure the file to customize
	the location of blender and the command.

	needs: [Ruby, unzip, curl]


    > w4

	Fetch the weather forecast from weather.gov.  For now you'll need to
	edit the file for your location.

	needs: [Ruby]


Navigation

    > fcd

	fuzzy cd. Interactive change directory starting at the current
	directory.

	needs: [fzf]

